$$ \boldsymbol{\gamma} =\frac{1}{{{{\boldsymbol{\lambda}}_0}\mathbf{exp}\left[ {\boldsymbol{\beta} \left( {\boldsymbol{PM}-\overline{\boldsymbol{PM}}} \right)} \right]}} $$
]]></EquationSource>
